targets.query: SELECT 100.0 - (mean("system") + mean("user")) FROM "cs_agent_cpu" WHERE "ip_address" =~ /^$IpAddress$/ AND "session" =~ /^$SessionId$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "ip_address" fill(null)

list.name: CS Agent Started Event
list.query: select status,ip_address,event from cs_agent_events where status=1 and ip_address =~ /$IpAddress$/ and $timeFilter

list.name: CS Agent Stopped Event
list.query: select status,ip_address,event from cs_agent_events where status=0 and ip_address =~ /$IpAddress$/ and $timeFilter
